      <title>日元下跌，债券期货上涨，因日本央行推迟公布债务购买细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/yen-drops-as-boj-says-to-specify-bond-buying-plan-at-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行表示将减少债务购买量但将细节推迟到下次政策会议后，日元走弱，日本主权债券价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/yen-drops-as-boj-says-to-specify-bond-buying-plan-at-next-month</guid>
